HEADWORD: Hackelia
<hw>Hackelia</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of plants with seeds
that stick to clothing, including stickseed and some of the beggar's
lice.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Hackelia</gen>, Lappula, genus
<gen>Lappula</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
